nodes.text: Star Wars Insider 144 is the 122nd issue of the magazine Star Wars Insider and the 52nd published by Titan Magazines. It was released on September 3, 2013.

Princess Leia takes center stage this issue as we look at what makes her tick! We'll also be taking an indepth look at the all-new comic book The Star Wars, which turns the once familiar saga on its head! Much-loved artist Jeffrey Brown offers a unique look at his forthcoming new comic book, Jedi Academy, and Star Wars: The Clone Wars' pirate Hondo Ohnaka stars in a unique adventure exclusively in Insider!
